data.description: **Offer Accepted! Still taking showings and Back-up offers! HIGHEST AND BEST! **Seller's are offering $$ in credits to buyers or to BUY-DOWN buyer's INTEREST rate! Enjoy the holidays in this lovely, renovated home with a big primary bathroom with double sinks, a tub, a separate stand-up shower, and a huge walk-in closet with lots of storage! The living room has vaulted ceilings and big windows letting in all of the natural sunlight, brightening up the open floor-plan home. Relax next to the cozy fireplace this winter season. The kitchen has NEW appliances, a breakfast nook/table area, breakfast bar, and a formal dining room- great for additional seating when you have guests over! Recessed lighting throughout. NEW flooring and A/C! Split floor plan with 2 other bedrooms on the left with a jack-and-jill bathroom in between! Separate utility room for your laundry. Backyard shed is included! Extremely low annual HOA costs, NO FLOOD ZONE, and close to tons of shopping and restaurants!
